translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「私は隊長の命令以外を聞く気はないわ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I have no intention of listening to anything other than the captain's orders."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今までそんなのなくても抱かれたろう」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You've been embraced even without that until now."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「今の私はあくまでも隊長の命令で動いてるわ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Right now, I'm only acting on the captain's orders.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 『今後は自由に闇の翼の為に動いていいです』
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The order was, 'From now on you are free to act for the Dark Wings as you see fit.'
That was the order, you see."
It was more like I gave you time off..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「総統に抱かれるのは命令の中に含まれてないの。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Being embraced by the Commander-in-Chief wasn't included in the orders.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: また隊長の命令があればいいのよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If the captain gives me another order, that will do."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 抱かれるべきと思うなら、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you think I should be embraced,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私に命令してくれるかしら」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: would you please give me that order?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私とランスの関係知りながら、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Knowing about the relationship between Lanse and me,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そんな命令出せなんて……」
私に命令してちょうだい。
「うわーん、ランスに抱かれてあげて下さいー！」
「あーあ、泣きながら行っちまった」

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "The Commander-in-Chief sure knows how to make women cry."
"You're the one who made her cry."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「というわけで隊長も連れてきたわ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "That's why I brought the captain too."
"Why do I have to come too!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私が総統に抱かれること」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: About me being embraced by the Commander-in-Chief."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「だったら、ここにいればいいじゃない」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "If so, then you should just stay here."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ほら、ちゃんと自分の口で言いなさい。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Come on, say it properly with your own mouth.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 隊長はどうさせて欲しいの？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What do you want the captain to do?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 口で言わなきゃ分からないわよ？　ん？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If you don't say it out loud, no one will know. Hm?"
